        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "As You Read",
        "bbox": [
          0.10029850746268656,
          0.04904214559386973,
          0.23243781094527363,
          0.06620689655172414
        ],
        "order": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_1",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Consider a conflict of interest you have encountered in your life. How did you resolve it?",
        "bbox": [
          0.0891542288557214,
          0.07172413793103448,
          0.25233830845771144,
          0.14835249042145593
        ],
        "order": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "When you encounter an ethical decision and must choose a course of action, ask yourself these important questions:",
        "bbox": [
          0.3088557213930348,
          0.07295019157088123,
          0.8453731343283583,
          0.10911877394636016
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_4",
        "observed_type": "list",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "• Is it against the law? Does it violate company or professional policies? • Even if everyone is doing it, how would I feel if someone did this to me? • Am I sacrifi cing long-term benefits for short-term gains?",
        "bbox": [
          0.3255721393034826,
          0.11524904214559387,
          0.8692537313432835,
          0.20904214559386974
        ],
        "order": 5
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0003",
    "kind": "section_text_panel",
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "primary_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_5",
    "source": "header_anchor",
    "member_count": 4,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_5",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "The Ethical Decision-Making Process",
        "bbox": [
          0.30646766169154227,
          0.229272030651341,
          0.7530348258706467,
          0.2519540229885057
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Here are some steps to take if you fi nd yourself in an ethical dilemma:",
        "bbox": [
          0.3072636815920398,
          0.2550191570881226,
          0.8390049751243781,
          0.2899616858237548
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_7",
        "observed_type": "index",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "1. Identify the ethical dilemma. 2. Discover alternative actions. 3. Decide who might be affected. 4. List the probable effects of the alternatives. 5. Select the best alternative.",
        "bbox": [
          0.32477611940298506,
          0.29670498084291186,
          0.7164179104477612,
          0.389272030651341
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Using this process will enable you to make a more informed ethical choice. Making an ethical decision involves more people than just you.",
        "bbox": [
          0.30646766169154227,
          0.39846743295019155,
          0.8573134328358208,
          0.4542528735632184
        ],
        "order": 9
      }
    ]
  },
